  <entry>
    <id>tag:github.com,2008:Grit::Commit/451a9a451531f57bbf5dc34bd7fe4be01343de7c</id>
    <link type="text/html" rel="alternate" href="https://github.com/chartjs/Chart.js/commit/451a9a451531f57bbf5dc34bd7fe4be01343de7c"/>
    <title>
        Fix #2418 Firefox old version compatibility
    </title>
    <updated>2016-05-25T22:39:42Z</updated>
    <media:thumbnail height="30" width="30" url="https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/3874900?s=30&amp;v=4"/>
    <author>
      <name>simonbrunel</name>
      <uri>https://github.com/simonbrunel</uri>
    </author>
    <content type="html">
      &lt;pre style=&#39;white-space:pre-wrap;width:81ex&#39;&gt;Fix #2418 Firefox old version compatibility

Old versions of FF doesn&amp;#39;t accept accessing the computed style via the &amp;#39;max-width&amp;#39; and &amp;#39;max-height&amp;#39; CSS notations using brackets, in which case the returned value is undefined. Changed the constraint methods to use maxWidth and mawHeight instead and make sure to test valid values.&lt;/pre&gt;
    </content>
  </entry>
